   " " Author[1] FORMAT "x(61)"                                  " ≥      0401108      ≥" SKIP
   " " Author[2] FORMAT "x(61)"                                  " ¿ƒƒƒƒƒƒƒƒƒƒƒƒƒƒƒƒƒƒƒŸ" SKIP
   " " Author[3] FORMAT "x(61)" SKIP(1)
   .
   IF AVAIL op THEN DO:
      {isispmem.i}
